Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有班级联欢会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把零食带来教室里吃也没关系的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没想到却发生了那样的事……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good Morning~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是转学生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫语吕五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是弹珠汽水的香气！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸酸甜甜的记忆 难以启齿爱的预感！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱就是LoveLove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love就要说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love&Peace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥气球给我狠狠地去死一死！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love不应该是这样来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就……咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀~看光光了~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不许看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也变得滚滚圆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为下一节是体育课
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先有穿上布鲁玛真是太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好个头哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 这个可真叫人大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨碌骨碌~
